title: Brown & Dana - It Was A Very Good Year [1963] {2008 Sail Mus
description:
Korean Exlcusive CD Release Housed in Mini LP Sleeve
LIMITED EDITION

Officially Released by SAIL MUSIC KOREA 2008

The Only Album of The Folksinging Duo Brown & Dana ,Achieved Great Sucess Among The College Crawd During `60s.
This Brilliant Debut Featuers `The Ace of Sorrrow`,Popular With Joan Baez`s Version.
`Wanderin`,Later Recorded By James Taylor And `It`s Was A Very Good Year`,Inspired Frank Sinatra`s Later Version.
The Treasure-trove and The Essential Album For Falk Collectors.
